{"tid":2515310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梅媽胃抽筋入院：打針鬆弛！","createTime":"2021-05-04T01:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T05:37:10.000Z","uid":281492,"like":81,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"00db0373774ad766661a1504f9fd70163bffd8d4","tid":2515310,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:40:53.000Z","msg":"現年97歲的梅艷芳母親覃美金因胃病入院，她接受訪問時表示：「冇事，只係少少胃痛，胃抽筋囉，以前都試過，醫生話休息兩日，要食胃藥，胃抽筋久唔久都有，今次抽得犀利，要打針鬆弛，依家好番好多啦，要煮爛啲嘢先食，但好攰，要瞓覺。」其實梅媽去年曾因心臟問題入院，進行通波仔手術。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY1HfgdnMGTHQz6ZmhjY7ABkHH5THC2ufYFkD3k2YxVNe?filename=YopwEfG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYopwEfG.png&h=0f1cbeca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梅媽話食咗胃藥，依家冇咩嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><span class=\"green\">白粉報唔貼link</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">屌你老母咁撚長命</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce532ea8ee72b33c92c6b6fd3f31e81e2cfd6810","tid":2515310,"uid":89382,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:41:46.000Z","msg":"科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f3de6b881140273f69fb39fd3b56e8fea9767a","tid":2515310,"uid":281492,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"ce532ea8ee72b33c92c6b6fd3f31e81e2cfd6810","tid":2515310,"uid":89382,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:41:46.000Z","msg":"科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:42:51.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢會命硬到打科興都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c9aaf8de55020bf30a10d0d066